:FED.
15.1 Coverage
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance policy covers personal injury if an insured person is the
victim of an assault. Payment of compensation is dependent on the insured
reporting the assault to the police.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
15.2 Compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance coverage amounts to up to DKK 250,000 per person. The
compensation payable is calculated according to the sum a perpetrator
deemed liable would be required to pay for similar actions under Danish
law.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
